featured_reviews.review_id: The structure of this masjid is quite good. It is one of the tallest buildings in Maniamore.The post office is located in front of it.This mosque is also visible to you from Rajendra Colony. The loudspeaker on top of the tower here opens automatically when it is visited at five in the morning. This place has become the hallmark of Toh Maniamore. This mosque is situated on the very edge of the main road of Maniamore, which will benefit those coming by road.
